Officers said all three victims had been drunk, and possibly drugged.  

Poindexter was convicted of sexually assaulting the four men this week and will be sentenced on March 20. 

Juror Jennifer Davis said the jury were 'disgusted to know that someone of that age' would prey on young adults.  

Poindexter was well-known on the tournament circuit and attended a number of beer pong competitions at bars throughout the D.C. and Baltimore area, as well as Atlantic City, Las Vegas, Dallas, Virginia Beach and Salt Lake City. 

Police have urged other potential victims to come forward and contact the Montgomery County Special Victims Unit.   

